[00:00.32]Phil Strongarm, the American astronaut has landed on the moon. He's speaking to Mission Control now:
[00:07.10]<b>Mission Control:</b> Hello, Phil... can you hear me?
[00:12.00]<b>Strongarm:</b> Yes, I can hear you clearly.
[00:15.54]<b>Mission Control:</b> What are you going to do next?
[00:17.73]<b>Strongarm:</b> I'm going to open the door.
[00:21.54]<b>Mission Control:</b> Hello, Phil... What are you doing now?
[00:25.92]<b>Strongarm:</b> I'm opening the door.
[00:30.06]<b>Mission Control:</b> Phil! Have you opened the door?
[00:33.60]<b>Strongarm:</b> Yes, I've opened the door. I can see the moon! It's fantastic!
[00:40.30]<br>